    Tarantulas made his way through the remains of the Cave. Paralysis and 
the others were back at base, but he slipped away. After all, he needed to 
keep busy and he didnt plan on staying under Aracnias claw forever.
    While looking for remains of bits of computers, he heard the voice of 
Darkmouse, injured and hurt. He walked over to her, looked around to see if 
anyone was watching, and then licked the mech flowing from her back. It was 
delicious...pure ecstacy. 
    But he did have to get her back to base. He lifted her up and started 
back for base, inhaling her wonderful smell the entire time.
